SIMPLE: hansom_cab
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hansom cab
<hw>Han"som cab`</hw> <pr>(k⟦acr⟧b`)</pr></mhw>. <ety>[From the name of
the inventor.]</ety> <def>A light, low, two-wheeled covered carriage
with the driver's seat elevated behind, the reins being passed over the
top.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He hailed a cruising <qex>hansom</qex> . . . ⟦ldquo⟧ 'Tis the
gondola of London,⟦rdquo⟧ said Lothair.</q>
<rj><qau>Beaconsfield.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Han't</ent>⟦br⟧
